import '../css/App.css';
import Index from './Index'
import Signup from './Signup'
import Login from './Login'
import Home from './Home'
import Myblogs from './Myblogs'
import Info from './Info'

const App = () => {

  const path = window.location.pathname

  switch (path) {
    case '/signup':
      return <Signup />

    case '/login':
      return <Login />

    case '/home':
      return <Home />

    case '/home/myblogs':
      return <Myblogs />

    case '/home/info':
      return <Info />

    default:
      return <Index />
  }

}

export default App;
